content.raw: Hi, I am trying to use this plugin in Gazebo 9 but the Actor.hh file is different and the [Actor.cc](http://Actor.cc) file doesn’t even exist \(I did a ros-melodic-desktop-full download\). I see above that you merged this branch with Gazebo 8. Is it possible that the changes weren’t carried over? Is there perhaps a new way to implement the actor collision properties in Gazebo 9 that I am missing? Thank you.
